        "id": "9cb8a0393b542e40000e722d"
      },
      "index": 0,
      "text": "We've just completed our orbital scans of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFarhome],Farhome]] III, and they've pretty much confirmed what we already knew. [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTerra],Terran]] planet in a near perfect orbit since it's the second largest planetoid in the system.\n\nHas the proper orbital inclination for seasonal weather and a moon for tidal waves, so evolution ran its course and we should find a complex ecosystem.",
