      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cf767bafedd51f2c81f231e"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Interesting that it was discovered so late, otherwise on the surface it seems to be a pretty standard Terran type. Since this wasn't a colonization mission, there must be something down there that got [[DM.Factions[faction_InterstellarExpeditions],IE]]'s attention.\n\nWhat about the atmospheric composition? Any signs of past or present civilization?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 2,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
