    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd0c317fc83df626eab6c00"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "If you plan on retiring down there, you'll likely die alone, either due a horrible local disease, the vegetation, or the wildlife.\n\nThese virgin natural worlds can still be very deadly for human colonists until their ecosystem is tamed. Sometimes it would be cheaper to just terraform another world with Terran species.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
