    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cc1e15bc94bb3892b598e00"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "I'll retire with an <i>[[DM.MechDefs[mechdef_atlas_AS7-D],Atlas]]</i> then. \n\nIf it's been already colonized, what if whomever lives down there is hiding underground and this is just a cover? Maybe they didn't like being found and disturbed by IE?",
      "branches": [
