    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c939a71cbbb4fd251a19aa3"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "We will cross that bridge when we reach it, Yang.\n\nSumire, what about the base camp for the Interstellar Expeditions party? Were you able to scan its location as well?",
      "branches": [
