    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c509ee091e14d4debd2677e"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Judging from the size of the signatures and their recorded speed, I'd say several meters in length and height. And there was a whole pack of them approaching the camp. \n\nYou wanted extraterrestrial aliens Yang. Now you have them.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Can these animals become a danger to us?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 10,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
