      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c32f7c30470e09760c277f1"
      },
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Our [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreBattleMech],BattleMechs]] will likely make them run away. \n\nThey're probably scavengers being attracted to the abandoned IE camp.",
