      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ca939719ae1550aaa8ab18f"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Commander, if I'm picking correctly Doctor Murad's meaning, that doesn't bode well for the lives of the scientists. Maybe all of them were already killed or eaten by those creatures or others. ",
