    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7d2a1ac207377279526ccb"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "That's possible but doubtful. If those animals had killed the IE team then they would be leaving the camp, not approaching it. \n\nWe haven't detected anything bigger, so it's more likely that the humans either left voluntarily or were forced to. Or even that they are still in that camp.",
      "branches": [
