      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cc529f7ac71539d5e352ac0"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Well the camp appears to be empty and without any power, not even an emergency beacon. \n\nAnd why would the resupply [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreJumpShip],JumpShip]] receive a distress signal but now they can't reply to our messages?\n\n",
      "branches": [
