        "id": "9c5f36580ec1f5bafaa8ab87"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "There's something rather strange here. This is sounding like one of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHolovidPeripheryTales],Periphery Tales]] novels, the one where the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreComStarExplorerCorps],Explorer Corps]] mission completely disappears...\n\nBut yeah, we should be cautious, just saying.",
